00:00:48,243 --> 00:00:53,403
O LjUBAVI I SENKAMA

4
00:02:19,042 --> 00:02:22,126
1973., moju zemlju, ile...

5
00:02:22,212 --> 00:02:24,880
preuzela je vojna hunta

6
00:02:24,881 --> 00:02:27,881
i proglasila stalno
vanredno stanje.

7
00:02:28,802 --> 00:02:31,258
Nametnut je policijski
as i gotovo svi,

8
00:02:31,259 --> 00:02:33,715
a posebno privilegovani...

9
00:02:33,807 --> 00:02:37,092
sami su sebi nametnuli
pravilo utanja.

10
00:02:37,769 --> 00:02:41,434
Pravilo: ne vidimo,
ne ujemo i ne govorimo o zlu,

11
00:02:41,982 --> 00:02:44,982
tako da je ivot mogao da se
nastavi kao do sada.

12
00:02:45,861 --> 00:02:48,070
Mojoj majci je to teko palo.

13
00:02:48,071 --> 00:02:51,606
Odrasla sam u bezbednosti
imanja Volje Boje.

14
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:54,285
Na dom je postao dom staraca...

15
00:02:54,286 --> 00:02:58,912
da bismo finansijski opstali posle
odlaska mog oca pre mnogo godina.

16
00:03:04,796 --> 00:03:09,458
Roza, moj pas, Kleo...

17
00:03:09,551 --> 00:03:13,845
I starci, Don Kihot, Pukovnik,
ovek koji smo zvali Smrt...

18
00:03:14,598 --> 00:03:18,132
i stara glumica,
madam Hosefina,

19
00:03:18,769 --> 00:03:21,769
bili su moja prava porodica.

20
00:03:21,897 --> 00:03:26,523
Bila sam verena za mog roaka
Gustava, kapetana u vojsci.

21
00:03:26,985 --> 00:03:29,945
Radila sam u modnom asopisu.

22
00:03:29,946 --> 00:03:32,490
O mom ivotu se brino
starala moja majka,

23
00:03:32,491 --> 00:03:35,694
odluna da mi nae
mesto u drutvu.

24
00:03:35,786 --> 00:03:39,404
Udajom za bogataa ili vojnika.

25
00:03:40,874 --> 00:03:43,042
ivot mi je bio bezbedan.

26
00:03:43,043 --> 00:03:46,003
Hajde. -Sve dok nisam
poela da se budim.

27
00:03:46,004 --> 00:03:49,004
Doi!

28
00:03:49,174 --> 00:03:52,092
Gledaj, belgijska ipka,

29
00:03:52,093 --> 00:03:57,254
francuska svila... irski lan,
upravo stiglo iz Brazila.

30
00:03:58,100 --> 00:04:00,618
Brazila?

31
00:04:00,619 --> 00:04:03,137
Rekla sam Rozi da sve
ovo stavi u tvoju sobu.

32
00:04:03,563 --> 00:04:06,563
Vreme je da se ti za ovo brine.

33
00:04:06,775 --> 00:04:09,775
Neu nikad da ih peglam.

34
00:04:12,739 --> 00:04:15,739
Gde ide, ako mogu da znam?

35
00:04:16,034 --> 00:04:18,160
Izlazim sa nekim prijateljima.

36
00:04:18,161 --> 00:04:21,161
A ako Gustavo pozove?

37
00:04:21,498 --> 00:04:24,498
Nee.

38
00:04:28,255 --> 00:04:31,255
Kapetan Gustavo Morante.

39
00:04:40,434 --> 00:04:43,637
Naredite, ser.
-Nalevo krug.

40
00:04:55,115 --> 00:04:58,115
Stoj!

41
00:04:59,578 --> 00:05:02,578
Pokai oruje.

42
00:05:10,422 --> 00:05:13,422
ekaj.

43
00:05:33,445 --> 00:05:35,592
Zaustavite kola, gdine.

44
00:05:35,593 --> 00:05:37,740
Mi smo iz Kardinalove
Komisije za ljudska prava.

45
00:05:37,741 --> 00:05:40,741
U redu je.

46
00:05:51,671 --> 00:05:54,671
Zdravo, Elena.

47
00:06:02,599 --> 00:06:05,599
Ovo je moj brat.

48
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:12,439
Jadnica, nije mogla da veruje...

49
00:06:30,752 --> 00:06:32,837
Zato?

50
00:06:32,838 --> 00:06:35,957
Hvala to ste doli, doktore.
Samo...

51
00:06:40,178 --> 00:06:43,178
Prosto ne mogu.

52
00:06:47,811 --> 00:06:50,604
Hajde.

53
00:06:50,605 --> 00:06:53,605
Reci.

54
00:06:54,025 --> 00:06:57,025
Zato?

55
00:06:59,614 --> 00:07:02,324
Poveli su nas i ubacili u...

56
00:07:02,325 --> 00:07:05,244
kamion.

57
00:07:05,245 --> 00:07:07,558
Tebe i...

58
00:07:07,559 --> 00:07:09,872
Mog mua, Huana.

59
00:07:10,917 --> 00:07:13,917
Vozili su nas satima.

60
00:07:14,546 --> 00:07:17,298
utirali...

61
00:07:17,299 --> 00:07:20,299
Pretili nam.

62
00:07:21,219 --> 00:07:23,679
Mogla sam da mislim samo...

63
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:26,680
na mog malog Gabriela,

64
00:07:27,392 --> 00:07:30,269
kod kue...

65
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:33,270
samog.

66
00:07:33,315 --> 00:07:36,315
elim samo da umrem.

67
00:07:36,902 --> 00:07:39,902
Zato nisam mrtva?
-Ne, ne...

68
00:07:40,947 --> 00:07:43,948
Mora da ivi.
Budi jaka.

69
00:07:45,702 --> 00:07:48,702
Mora da se bori.

70
00:07:52,501 --> 00:07:56,830
Razdvojili su nas i rekli
su mi da ako ne saraujem...

71
00:07:58,006 --> 00:08:01,006
platie moj mu.

72
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:04,428
A onda...

73
00:08:04,429 --> 00:08:07,429
pipao me je rukama...

74
00:08:07,599 --> 00:08:10,599
svuda po telu.

75
00:08:11,061 --> 00:08:14,181
Mislila sam samo
na ivot mog mua.

76
00:08:16,817 --> 00:08:20,565
Nisam htela da uje.

77
00:08:25,534 --> 00:08:28,534
Vratio se...

78
00:08:29,162 --> 00:08:32,162
Drugi glas...

79
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:36,999
Jo ruku svuda po meni...

80
00:08:45,637 --> 00:08:48,637
U meni.

81
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:53,559
Htela sam da vritim.

82
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:59,440
Ali nisam htela
da moj mu to uje.

83
00:09:01,027 --> 00:09:04,027
Nastavilo se opet i opet.

84
00:09:05,657 --> 00:09:08,657
Pusti to, ne misli.

85
00:09:10,287 --> 00:09:13,287
Videemo se sledee nedelje.

86
00:09:17,377 --> 00:09:20,377
Bog vas blagoslovio.

87
00:09:30,307 --> 00:09:33,307
Mogu li da vam pomognem?

88
00:09:35,312 --> 00:09:38,312
Na crnoj listi je.

89
00:09:42,027 --> 00:09:44,737
Mogu li da vidim Irenu?
-Molim?

90
00:09:44,738 --> 00:09:46,906
Irenu Beltrao.

91
00:09:46,907 --> 00:09:49,074
Irenu? -Da.

92
00:09:49,075 --> 00:09:52,075
Ovuda.

93
00:09:53,038 --> 00:09:56,038
Plavue su ove godine u modi.

94
00:09:58,627 --> 00:10:01,663
Preneu to na drutvenu stranicu.

95
00:10:03,048 --> 00:10:06,048
O, ko je to?

96
00:10:15,143 --> 00:10:17,186
Francisko Leal?
-Gospoice Beltrao.

97
00:10:17,187 --> 00:10:20,187
Irena.

98
00:10:20,357 --> 00:10:23,523
itao sam vae lanke i...
-Vi ste fotograf.

99
00:10:26,363 --> 00:10:29,363
Izvinite, moram da pitam.

100
00:10:29,658 --> 00:10:32,658
Jeste li na nekoj listi?
-Nisam.

101
00:10:32,828 --> 00:10:35,454
Nisam na crnoj listi.

102
00:10:35,455 --> 00:10:38,455
Onda moemo da priamo.
-Svakako.

103
00:10:39,417 --> 00:10:42,751
Pokazau vam svoje radove.

104
00:10:58,603 --> 00:11:01,603
Jeste li gladni?
-Gladan?

105
00:11:02,732 --> 00:11:05,732
Doite.

106
00:11:10,949 --> 00:11:13,949
Koji od mojih lanaka
vam se najvie svia?

107
00:11:17,789 --> 00:11:20,956
"Super hormoni -
prevencija trudnoe."

108
00:11:21,042 --> 00:11:23,043
Veoma zanimljivo.

109
00:11:23,044 --> 00:11:26,547
Stvarno? -Da.
Napisali ste...

110
00:11:26,548 --> 00:11:29,548
"Koncepcija je akt pobune."

111
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:34,839
Od 73. asopis mora da pokrije
gole grudi crnim trakama.

112
00:11:36,057 --> 00:11:39,057
A odreene rei su zabranjene.

113
00:11:39,478 --> 00:11:42,478
Na primer?

114
00:11:42,522 --> 00:11:44,690
Detinjasto je.

115
00:11:44,691 --> 00:11:46,817
"Abortus."

116
00:11:46,818 --> 00:11:49,028
"Guza."

117
00:11:49,029 --> 00:11:52,029
"Sloboda"?

118
00:12:13,595 --> 00:12:16,715
Znai, vi ste psiholog.

119
00:12:18,141 --> 00:12:21,510
Frojdovac?
-Frojd, Jung.

120
00:12:23,313 --> 00:12:26,313
Marks.
-Marks?

121
00:12:27,317 --> 00:12:29,819
I on je pisao o psihologiji?

122
00:12:29,820 --> 00:12:32,820
O lanoj svesti.

123
00:12:32,823 --> 00:12:37,864
Napisao je: "Sramota je jedino
Revolucionarno oseanje."

124
00:12:38,620 --> 00:12:41,620
Jeste li sigurni da niste
na crnoj listi?

125
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:50,420
Moj otac je anarhista.

126
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:54,550
Pobegao je iz panije.

127
00:12:55,595 --> 00:12:58,881
Moda je moj brat, svetenik?

128
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:05,719
Moda i moj stariji
brat, Havijer, profesor?

129
00:13:08,942 --> 00:13:11,942
Ali ne ja.

130
00:13:12,279 --> 00:13:15,197
Ali ta...
-Od 73., moja vrsta psihologije

131
00:13:15,198 --> 00:13:19,030
je postala tabu i nedostupna.

132
00:13:24,833 --> 00:13:27,833
Traim samo pristojan posao.

133
00:13:28,712 --> 00:13:32,211
Ne elim da zavrim slikajui
roendane i venanja.

134
00:13:35,469 --> 00:13:38,262
Doite po mene sutra u
Volju Boju.

135
00:13:38,263 --> 00:13:41,263
Imau zadatak za vas.
-Hvala.

136
00:13:45,145 --> 00:13:48,145
Ne. Nezapoljeni ste.
Platiu ja. -Molim vas.

137
00:13:48,482 --> 00:13:52,526
Otac nas je uio da ljubaznost
nikad nije spreila anarhiju.

138
00:13:58,325 --> 00:14:01,325
Ja u.

139
00:14:04,164 --> 00:14:06,791
Uite.
-Ko je to?

140
00:14:06,792 --> 00:14:09,502
U mojoj kui?

141
00:14:09,503 --> 00:14:12,087
Ovo je stil Volje Boje.

142
00:14:12,088 --> 00:14:15,374
Mama, ovo je Dr...
-Dobar dan.

143
00:14:18,053 --> 00:14:20,346
Francisko, ovo je moja mama.

144
00:14:20,347 --> 00:14:23,632
Mama, ovo je moj kolega, Dr Leal.
-Kolega?

145
00:14:24,476 --> 00:14:27,311
Doktor? -Da, ali Francisko
sada radi kao fotograf

146
00:14:27,312 --> 00:14:30,312
i treba da mu naem posao.

147
00:14:32,150 --> 00:14:34,902
Stiglo je neto
za tebe od Gustava.

148
00:14:34,903 --> 00:14:37,071
Bie ovde za vikend.

149
00:14:37,072 --> 00:14:40,073
Nisam otvorila,
bila je poruka i za mene.

150
00:14:40,158 --> 00:14:43,741
Kapetan Morante i Irena
e uskoro da se venaju.

151
00:14:44,371 --> 00:14:46,809
Roza.
-ta?

152
00:14:46,810 --> 00:14:49,248
Roen kao cvrak,
cvrae do smrti.

153
00:14:50,001 --> 00:14:52,711
Uvek tako govori!

154
00:14:52,712 --> 00:14:56,757
A sada e ceo dan da
ita romane i jede!

155
00:14:57,217 --> 00:15:00,217
Lepota znai zdrav izgled.

156
00:15:04,182 --> 00:15:06,371
Oh, a gde danas ide?

157
00:15:06,372 --> 00:15:08,561
Idemo do Los Riskosa da
intervjuiemo sveca.

158
00:15:08,562 --> 00:15:10,604
Kau da ini uda.

159
00:15:10,605 --> 00:15:12,982
A kakva to uda?

160
00:15:12,983 --> 00:15:16,186
Lei nesanicu i tucavicu,
tei slomljena srca...

161
00:15:16,278 --> 00:15:19,278
donosi kiu i vraa mladost.

162
00:15:20,031 --> 00:15:24,693
Ako ivi sveci lee,
mrtvi mogu da odmaraju.

163
00:15:45,182 --> 00:15:48,348
Svia mi se ovo!
Kao letei konj!

164
00:15:51,229 --> 00:15:53,439
Ko je Gustavo?

165
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:56,440
ta?
-Tvoj verenik.

166
00:15:57,861 --> 00:16:01,775
Moj roak.
Vereni smo od detinjstva.

167
00:16:03,784 --> 00:16:06,202
Ne zvui mi ozbiljno.

168
00:16:06,203 --> 00:16:09,203
Moj kapetan je veoma ozbiljan.

169
00:16:09,331 --> 00:16:12,331
Bie general jednog dana.

170
00:16:13,043 --> 00:16:16,043
Kad odraste.

171
00:16:17,130 --> 00:16:19,799
On je prava mukarina.

172
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:23,594
ta je to? -Nauiu te njegovu
pesmu. -Neka, hvala.

173
00:16:23,595 --> 00:16:26,138
"Ja sam mladoenja smrti"

174
00:16:26,139 --> 00:16:29,139
"Zaljubih se u hrabrost"

175
00:16:29,184 --> 00:16:32,184
"Koja je moj saputnik."

176
00:16:39,027 --> 00:16:41,111
To je pesma faista.

177
00:16:41,112 --> 00:16:43,614
Nije.
-Jeste.

178
00:16:43,615 --> 00:16:46,615
Otkud zna?

179
00:16:47,619 --> 00:16:49,954
Od oca.

180
00:16:49,955 --> 00:16:52,955
Frankovi faisti su ga
najurili iz panije.

181
00:16:53,792 --> 00:16:56,023
"ivela Smrt."

182
00:16:56,024 --> 00:16:58,254
To im je bio moto.

183
00:16:58,255 --> 00:17:01,789
Gustavo nije faista.
-Nije mladoenja smrti?

184
00:17:02,676 --> 00:17:05,676
Nije.

185
00:17:28,034 --> 00:17:31,034
Da li ovde ivi
Evanhelina Rankil?

186
00:17:31,079 --> 00:17:34,365
Da, ali uda ini u podne.

187
00:17:39,254 --> 00:17:41,839
Ona tamo...

188
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:44,758
Ona je svetica.
-Ne izgleda kao svetica, mama.

189
00:17:44,759 --> 00:17:48,627
Sveci su uobiajeni u selima.
Nije neka pria.

190
00:17:48,722 --> 00:17:51,722
Ali e proi cenzuru.

191
00:17:57,351 --> 00:17:59,523
Devojka je luda.
Prosto.

192
00:17:59,524 --> 00:18:03,273
A uda? -O kakvim
udima govorite?

193
00:18:03,445 --> 00:18:06,238
Ne verujte propagandi.

194
00:18:06,239 --> 00:18:10,319
Ono to treba toj
devojci je mukarac!

195
00:18:12,871 --> 00:18:15,871
Tako izgleda svetica?

196
00:18:16,958 --> 00:18:19,958
12 sati.

197
00:18:28,929 --> 00:18:31,722
Tako je bleda. Pogledaj.

198
00:18:31,723 --> 00:18:34,723
Tiho.

199
00:18:54,454 --> 00:18:57,454
Gledaj.

200
00:19:21,606 --> 00:19:24,442
Izlei moje noge, svetice!

201
00:19:24,443 --> 00:19:27,278
Ne dozvoli da odvedu
mog Huana u vojsku!

202
00:19:27,779 --> 00:19:30,547
Bog te blagoslovio,
Evanhelina!

203
00:19:30,548 --> 00:19:33,315
Izlei mog mua,
molim te! Preklinjem te!

204
00:19:36,413 --> 00:19:39,616
Brzo, brzo. Pokret!
Svi uza zid!

205
00:19:43,628 --> 00:19:45,671
Vaa dokumenta!

206
00:19:45,672 --> 00:19:48,756
Ja sam novinarka a on
je moj fotograf.

207
00:19:49,885 --> 00:19:52,386
Ime?

208
00:19:52,387 --> 00:19:56,515
Francisko Leal.
Koj kurac radi ovde?

209
00:19:56,516 --> 00:19:58,642
ta ste rekli?

210
00:19:58,643 --> 00:20:01,020
Ne obraam se tebi.

211
00:20:01,021 --> 00:20:04,021
Ali ja se obraam
vama, komandire.

212
00:20:05,442 --> 00:20:08,811
Pradeljo!
-Gospodine!

213
00:20:09,196 --> 00:20:12,196
Ovo je tvoja sestra?

214
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:16,200
Jeste.

215
00:20:29,007 --> 00:20:32,542
ta to radite?
uda nisu nikog ubila.

216
00:20:32,636 --> 00:20:35,886
Ne budi tako nervozna, duo.
Pucali smo u vazduh.

217
00:20:35,972 --> 00:20:38,891
Ne zovi me duom.
Zato ste ovde?

218
00:20:38,892 --> 00:20:41,435
Pradeljo mi je priao
o svojoj sestri.

219
00:20:41,436 --> 00:20:44,686
Radi neto o emu doktori i
svetenici nemaju pojma.

220
00:20:44,773 --> 00:20:47,940
Pa rekoh, ovo je posao za vojsku.

221
00:20:50,821 --> 00:20:53,821
Ne dirajte je!

222
00:20:54,407 --> 00:20:57,407
Doi ovamo.

223
00:21:38,743 --> 00:21:41,780
U stroj, budale!

224
00:21:41,872 --> 00:21:44,872
Narednie Faustino Rivera!

225
00:21:45,792 --> 00:21:48,792
Fotoaparat!

226
00:22:04,563 --> 00:22:09,935
Evanhelina...
-udo je da nas nisu pobili!

227
00:22:14,112 --> 00:22:17,279
Oprostite, preasni.
elite li jo limunade?

228
00:22:18,017 --> 00:22:22,316
Boe sauvaj nas...
-I zatiti.

229
00:22:33,799 --> 00:22:37,748
Videli smo malo pucanja u
vazduh i preplaene svinje.

230
00:22:40,788 --> 00:22:44,051
Slikaemo drugi put.

231
00:23:19,469 --> 00:23:22,263
ta emo ovde?
-Kampujemo.

232
00:23:22,264 --> 00:23:25,264
Ki, nadrealizam.

233
00:23:26,486 --> 00:23:28,833
Drutvo spektakla.

234
00:23:28,834 --> 00:23:31,834
Je l' to Marks ili Frojd, doktore?
-Gde si bila do sada?

235
00:23:33,002 --> 00:23:35,707
A gde ti misli?

236
00:23:35,708 --> 00:23:38,168
Kod mladoenje smrti.

237
00:23:38,169 --> 00:23:40,754
Neto si ogoren?

238
00:23:40,755 --> 00:23:43,632
Izvini... izvini.

239
00:23:43,633 --> 00:23:46,343
Samo sam hteo da te
pozovem na veeru...

240
00:23:46,344 --> 00:23:49,344
U utorak? Biu slobodna.

241
00:23:49,556 --> 00:23:53,090
Hoe? Stvarno?
-ta?

242
00:23:54,143 --> 00:23:57,143
Bie slobodna?

243
00:24:06,489 --> 00:24:10,783
Gustavo, ide za Panamu?
-Da.

244
00:24:12,328 --> 00:24:15,328
Ali vratiu se brzo.

245
00:24:15,373 --> 00:24:18,374
Kapetane Morante,
ovo je Dr Leal.

246
00:24:20,879 --> 00:24:25,375
Grofice! Svetlo nestaje.
Sve bledi. Moramo...

247
00:24:27,051 --> 00:24:30,337
Mario, da li si upoznao
Franciska Leala?

248
00:24:30,430 --> 00:24:32,598
Radi za mene.

249
00:24:32,599 --> 00:24:35,475
Drago mi je.
-I meni.

250
00:24:35,476 --> 00:24:38,352
A ovo je moj verenik, kapetan
Morante. Ovo je zloglasni Mario.

251
00:24:42,442 --> 00:24:45,811
Izvinite, ne rukujem se
sa... degenericima.

252
00:24:47,572 --> 00:24:50,490
Zato ne elite da je
dodirnete, kapetane?

253
00:24:50,491 --> 00:24:52,993
Moda je vaa
gruba spoljanost

254
00:24:52,994 --> 00:24:56,114
samo maska za
homoseksualnu paniku?

255
00:24:57,457 --> 00:25:00,457
Videemo se ujutro.

256
00:25:05,757 --> 00:25:08,757
Faista!

257
00:25:14,599 --> 00:25:17,599
Lepi...

258
00:25:18,144 --> 00:25:21,104
veeras kuvam
italijansku hranu.

259
00:25:21,105 --> 00:25:23,232
Pasta marinata.

260
00:25:23,233 --> 00:25:26,233
Verujem da si slobodan.

261
00:25:26,778 --> 00:25:29,778
Valjda jesam.

262
00:25:30,949 --> 00:25:33,367
Vov Kliko Ponarden.

263
00:25:33,368 --> 00:25:36,368
La Grand Dam, 1969.

264
00:25:37,705 --> 00:25:40,705
Mnogo... pokradeno.

265
00:25:40,917 --> 00:25:46,077
Od ena i ljubavnica generala
koje sam minkao i mazao,

266
00:25:46,172 --> 00:25:50,004
etkao, eljao i hipnotisao,

267
00:25:50,134 --> 00:25:53,883
ubeujui da su najlepe
ene na svetu.

268
00:25:55,974 --> 00:26:00,470
Jer sam inio da sebe vide
onakvim kakve ele da budu.

269
00:26:04,190 --> 00:26:07,190
Za iluzije.

270
00:26:09,779 --> 00:26:12,739
Za stvarnost.

271
00:26:12,740 --> 00:26:16,323
Prostitutka mi je spasila
ivot a ne crkva.

272
00:26:18,997 --> 00:26:24,704
Jo prie o tebi
i o tvojoj konkubini admirala.

273
00:26:30,091 --> 00:26:32,801
Moj brat me je odveo u bordel...

274
00:26:32,802 --> 00:26:36,385
na inicijaciju.

275
00:26:37,765 --> 00:26:42,474
Potpuno sam se uspaniio kad su
me ostavili nasamo sa njom.

276
00:26:44,063 --> 00:26:48,809
Sela je na krevet do mene
i drala me za ruku.

277
00:26:51,112 --> 00:26:53,739
Rekla mi je...

278
00:26:53,740 --> 00:26:57,156
"Na ovo niko ne moe
da te natera."

279
00:26:59,913 --> 00:27:02,913
Bio sam prestravljen.

280
00:27:03,249 --> 00:27:05,667
"Idi,

281
00:27:05,668 --> 00:27:10,544
"daleko, deko, jer ako
ostane, ubie te na kraju."

282
00:27:11,424 --> 00:27:14,591
Razumem.
-Spasila mi je ivot.

283
00:27:17,805 --> 00:27:22,681
"Ako se ne zaljubi,
idi to dalje moe."

284
00:27:26,523 --> 00:27:29,856
I... koliko si daleko iao?
-Vidi...

285
00:27:31,778 --> 00:27:34,778
vojska prezire ovakve ljude.

286
00:27:36,824 --> 00:27:40,692
Ali sam i dalje
nasmeen i posluan.

287
00:27:41,579 --> 00:27:44,579
Shvatam.

288
00:27:47,043 --> 00:27:51,290
Jednog dana bih mogao biti
izvuen iz svog salona u palati...

289
00:27:52,131 --> 00:27:55,251
i baen u jednu od
njihovih soba za muenje.

290
00:28:02,475 --> 00:28:05,475
Mogu li da ti kaem
neto u poverenju?

291
00:28:07,063 --> 00:28:09,356
Molim te.

292
00:28:09,357 --> 00:28:12,357
Diplomirani sam
psiholog, je l' tako?

293
00:28:13,027 --> 00:28:17,571
Da, Irena mi je rekla.
-Sada radim kao foto novinar.

294
00:28:17,657 --> 00:28:22,034
Da. -Takoe sam
jo neto drugo.

295
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:28,790
ta si?

296
00:28:30,295 --> 00:28:33,295
Radim u senkama.

297
00:28:35,633 --> 00:28:38,633
Zna li ta to znai?

298
00:28:43,099 --> 00:28:46,099
Doite deco.
Ujak ima gosta.

299
00:28:59,449 --> 00:29:02,449
Zdravo. Ui.

300
00:29:04,913 --> 00:29:08,578
Pomirii.
Kafa iz Venecuele.

301
00:29:10,877 --> 00:29:13,877
Hvala.

302
00:29:15,423 --> 00:29:18,423
Irena Beltrao... moja porodica.

303
00:29:18,635 --> 00:29:25,397
I Havijer. -Lepa je, tata.
-Lepa, da.

304
00:29:30,349 --> 00:29:33,800
U pono me budi da joj
recitujem Nerudu.

305
00:29:34,651 --> 00:29:39,728
Kad smo bili mladi, u paniji,
uestvovao sam u graanskom ratu.

306
00:29:40,573 --> 00:29:45,484
Kad sam krenuo na front, zakljuala
je kuu i krenula za mnom.

307
00:29:46,329 --> 00:29:50,706
Htela sam da budem s njim u
pobedi, porazu ili smrti.

308
00:29:50,792 --> 00:29:53,544
Da, prava ljubav.
Koja se zavrila...

309
00:29:53,545 --> 00:29:56,711
Hoze, ne poinji.
- sa naprslinom lobanje...

310
00:29:56,798 --> 00:29:59,464
i gubitkom pamenja.

311
00:29:59,465 --> 00:30:02,130
A sin, Havijer, rodio se
u ruevinama manastira.

312
00:30:02,220 --> 00:30:06,597
On je trebao da bude svetenik a ne ti.
-Dosta je bilo, doneu veeru.

313
00:30:07,684 --> 00:30:10,768
itala sam tvoje lanke.
Nasmejali su me.

314
00:30:15,942 --> 00:30:18,942
Oeni je, Francisko.

315
00:30:19,529 --> 00:30:22,529
Ve ima verenika, mama.

316
00:30:28,288 --> 00:30:31,538
Budi muko a ne psiholog, sine.

317
00:30:32,917 --> 00:30:35,917
Pourimo pre nego je oteraju.

318
00:30:37,422 --> 00:30:40,422
Irena, vidi li ovaj lenjir?

319
00:30:40,550 --> 00:30:43,343
To je jedina stvar koju
sam poneo u egzil.

320
00:30:43,344 --> 00:30:45,429
Pripadao je mom ocu.

321
00:30:45,430 --> 00:30:49,262
Bavio se rekonstrukcijom kua
i kopanjem rovova.

322
00:30:49,392 --> 00:30:53,224
A emu je ovo sluilo?
-Da izmeri zlobu i korupciju.

323
00:30:54,439 --> 00:30:58,021
Za nekog ko je pobegao od
jedne diktature a ivi u drugoj,

324
00:30:58,109 --> 00:31:01,478
mrnja prema vlasti je
ozbiljan nedostatak.

325
00:31:01,571 --> 00:31:05,651
Malo sam prestar da
hodam podvijenog repa.

326
00:31:05,742 --> 00:31:08,535
Morali smo da uklonimo njegovu
tamparsku presu iz kuhinje.

327
00:31:08,536 --> 00:31:11,988
Teko bismo je opravdali
pri policijskoj raciji.

328
00:31:12,290 --> 00:31:17,415
Ako ti se desi neto,
staviu glavu u rernu i umreti.

329
00:31:17,503 --> 00:31:19,546
Zato pazim ta radim.

330
00:31:19,547 --> 00:31:22,963
Zato smo uklonili presu
za tampanje, tata.

331
00:31:26,679 --> 00:31:29,679
Ali uskoro emo se
vratiti u paniju.

332
00:31:29,891 --> 00:31:32,891
Je l' tako, Havijer?

333
00:31:38,024 --> 00:31:41,024
Franko je umro, tata.
Moe odmah da se vrati.

334
00:31:42,654 --> 00:31:45,773
Za paniju.
-Za paniju.

335
00:31:47,158 --> 00:31:50,158
"Ali majica Zemlja je mrana,

336
00:31:51,788 --> 00:31:55,536
i duboko u meni i
ja sam mraan.

337
00:31:57,126 --> 00:31:59,711
Ja sam bunar.

338
00:31:59,712 --> 00:32:01,797
I u vodi...

339
00:32:01,798 --> 00:32:04,550
no ostavlja zvezde

340
00:32:04,551 --> 00:32:07,469
i ide dalje preko polja."

341
00:32:07,470 --> 00:32:10,010
Bakice, ne elim da idem...

342
00:32:10,011 --> 00:32:12,550
"Pitanje je da li
smo toliko iveli

343
00:32:12,934 --> 00:32:15,935
da elim jo
toliko da ivim."

344
00:32:16,104 --> 00:32:18,939
"Nikad mi glas nije
bio tako jasan.

345
00:32:18,940 --> 00:32:22,724
Nikad nije bio toliko
obogaen... poljupcima."

346
00:32:35,456 --> 00:32:38,456
Pokuaj da dobije imena
muitelja, Francisko.

347
00:32:39,669 --> 00:32:42,669
Valjda sam se onesvestila.

348
00:32:43,965 --> 00:32:46,466
A onda sam videla...

349
00:32:46,467 --> 00:32:49,467
Huana pored mene,

350
00:32:53,725 --> 00:32:57,259
kako visi sa kuke, kao i ja.

351
00:32:59,772 --> 00:33:02,772
Muili su nas oboje.

352
00:33:04,694 --> 00:33:09,356
Huana vie nego mene, ali...

353
00:33:12,785 --> 00:33:16,486
Ne prekidaj, Maria Elena.
Hajde, reci mi.

354
00:33:19,584 --> 00:33:21,627
Gabriel je bio tamo.

355
00:33:21,628 --> 00:33:26,586
Moj sin... u sobi
za muenje... moj mali sin.

356
00:33:27,717 --> 00:33:31,964
Drali su ga za ruke
i terali da gleda.

357
00:33:34,015 --> 00:33:39,175
"Ako nam ne kae imena,
i njega emo muiti."

358
00:33:40,230 --> 00:33:42,981
Nisam znala nikakva imena.

359
00:33:42,982 --> 00:33:45,982
Nikad nisam znala.

360
00:33:49,614 --> 00:33:52,614
Izmislila sam imena
koja nikad nisam znala.

361
00:33:53,993 --> 00:33:56,328
Nisam mogla vie.

362
00:33:56,329 --> 00:33:59,329
Ne vie.

363
00:33:59,749 --> 00:34:02,167
Otac Leal ne moe da ih nae.

364
00:34:02,168 --> 00:34:05,168
Otac Leal e nastaviti da trai.

365
00:34:05,505 --> 00:34:08,505
Svi emo.

366
00:34:09,008 --> 00:34:12,008
Bie sve u redu.

367
00:34:15,056 --> 00:34:18,056
Mora da brine o sebi.

368
00:34:18,142 --> 00:34:20,811
Bori se i budi jaka.

369
00:34:20,812 --> 00:34:23,689
I zapamti:

370
00:34:23,690 --> 00:34:26,690
nemoj da zaboravi.

371
00:34:27,402 --> 00:34:29,861
I nama su potrebna imena.

372
00:34:29,862 --> 00:34:34,939
Zato da se to nikada
vie ne desi. Nikada vie.

373
00:34:38,288 --> 00:34:42,831
Trebaju nam imena da bismo
se tiho borili protiv njih.

374
00:34:58,975 --> 00:35:01,975
Mora da nam da imena.

375
00:35:56,366 --> 00:35:58,617
Kako to da si slobodna u nedelju?

376
00:35:58,618 --> 00:36:01,618
Moj verenik ne moe
da doe za vikend.

377
00:36:01,621 --> 00:36:05,666
Dolazi svakog vikenda?
-Ne, ne svakog.

378
00:36:06,292 --> 00:36:09,292
A majka te ne puta da ode...
gde ono bee?

379
00:36:09,379 --> 00:36:12,379
Panama.
-U Panamu?

380
00:36:12,882 --> 00:36:17,425
Doktore, ne misli valjda da sam
u mojim godinama jo devica?

381
00:36:28,856 --> 00:36:31,066
ta se desilo?

382
00:36:31,067 --> 00:36:34,067
Recite mi, molim vas.

383
00:36:36,447 --> 00:36:38,949
Odveo ju je.

384
00:36:38,950 --> 00:36:41,950
Ko?
-Komandir.

385
00:36:43,663 --> 00:36:47,114
A moj sin...
Pradeljo je uhapen.

386
00:36:49,502 --> 00:36:52,502
Faustino Rivera je
imao suze u oima.

387
00:36:52,797 --> 00:36:55,215
Ko?

388
00:36:55,216 --> 00:36:58,216
Faustino Rivera, narednik.

389
00:36:59,429 --> 00:37:02,513
Znam ga od malena.

390
00:37:04,434 --> 00:37:07,352
Drao je pse...

391
00:37:07,353 --> 00:37:10,639
dok je Ramirez vukao do dipa.
-Boe.

392
00:37:14,152 --> 00:37:17,152
Nigde ne moemo da je naemo.

393
00:37:18,781 --> 00:37:21,781
Siromani smo.

394
00:37:22,535 --> 00:37:25,535
Ne znamo ta da radimo.

395
00:37:29,083 --> 00:37:32,083
Nai emo je.

396
00:37:33,213 --> 00:37:36,419
Pomoi u vam.

397
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:39,625
Te rei su mi promenile ivot
zauvek, a moje putovanje je poelo.

398
00:37:39,719 --> 00:37:42,507
Evanhelina Rankileo...

399
00:37:42,508 --> 00:37:45,295
odvedena je u Los Riskos na
ispitivanje i nije vie viena.

400
00:37:47,143 --> 00:37:49,770
Obratite se Ministarstvu Odbrane.

401
00:37:49,771 --> 00:37:52,771
Tamo imaju novu listu.

402
00:37:54,984 --> 00:37:57,984
Sledei.

403
00:38:06,996 --> 00:38:09,996
Vratite se sledee
nedelje u isto vreme.

404
00:38:17,423 --> 00:38:20,875
Ne gubite vreme.
Idite pravo u mrtvanicu.

405
00:38:22,095 --> 00:38:25,095
Irena, bolje ekaj ovde.

406
00:38:25,223 --> 00:38:27,558
Zato?

407
00:38:27,559 --> 00:38:32,185
Jesi li ikada videla mrtvaka?
Unakaeno i mueno telo?

408
00:38:32,730 --> 00:38:35,730
Nisam.
-Ne mora da ide.

409
00:38:35,817 --> 00:38:38,817
Idem.

410
00:38:41,322 --> 00:38:44,322
Hanibale, idemo dole.

411
00:39:25,450 --> 00:39:27,743
Irena.
-Francisko, izvedi je napolje.

412
00:39:27,744 --> 00:39:30,744
To nije ona.
Irena, nemogue je da je ona!

413
00:39:43,218 --> 00:39:46,421
Ne traimo je vie.
Nije ovde.

414
00:39:49,641 --> 00:39:52,641
Trebalo bi da se
vratimo u kancelariju.

415
00:39:58,775 --> 00:40:01,775
I ja tako mislim.

416
00:40:20,672 --> 00:40:23,672
Gustavo me je ekao
celog ivota.

417
00:40:25,009 --> 00:40:27,135
Udau se za njega.

418
00:40:27,136 --> 00:40:29,638
Znam.

419
00:40:29,639 --> 00:40:32,639
Hou.

420
00:41:19,230 --> 00:41:24,391
Nikada se neemo vratiti u
paniju bez tebe, Havijere Leal.

421
00:41:27,989 --> 00:41:30,990
"Toliko sam toga preiveo,
da e jednog dana...

422
00:41:31,951 --> 00:41:34,952
morati da me zaborave, silom,

423
00:41:35,997 --> 00:41:38,997
izbrisati me sa crne table...

424
00:41:39,417 --> 00:41:42,417
srce mi je bilo neumorno."

425
00:42:07,278 --> 00:42:10,278
Ono to si jue
videla je bio moj brat.

426
00:42:10,531 --> 00:42:13,531
Unitili su ga.

427
00:42:14,452 --> 00:42:18,532
Ubili su ga, ubivi
sve to je mu vredelo.

428
00:42:20,792 --> 00:42:23,792
Oduzeli su mu posao, sindikat,

429
00:42:24,254 --> 00:42:27,254
prijatelje, prihode, ponos,

430
00:42:28,466 --> 00:42:31,466
snagu.

431
00:42:33,429 --> 00:42:36,429
Vratiu se u Los Riskos.

432
00:42:39,686 --> 00:42:42,686
Idem kolima moje majke.
Odluila sam.

433
00:42:46,859 --> 00:42:51,237
Dobro pazi ta govori,
ak i svojoj majci.

434
00:42:54,701 --> 00:42:57,281
Digna mi je rekla gde da naem

435
00:42:57,282 --> 00:42:59,861
komandira Ramireza
i narednika Faustina.

436
00:43:01,583 --> 00:43:04,868
Da im se suprotstavim, trebala mi je
samo arogancija moje klase.

437
00:43:04,961 --> 00:43:08,128
Dovedena je samo zbog
rutinskog ispitivanja.

438
00:43:08,214 --> 00:43:12,342
Provela je no ovde
i putena je ujutro.

439
00:43:12,594 --> 00:43:14,887
Imamo izvetaj.

440
00:43:14,888 --> 00:43:18,007
Pustili ste je na ulicu bez odee?

441
00:43:18,099 --> 00:43:21,468
Graanka Rankileo je
imala cipele i pono.

442
00:43:21,561 --> 00:43:24,811
Maloletna je. Zato nije
vraena roditeljima?

443
00:43:24,898 --> 00:43:28,432
Ne moram da raspravljam o
policijskoj proceduri sa vama.

444
00:43:29,444 --> 00:43:31,591
Da li biste o njima
raspravljali sa

445
00:43:31,592 --> 00:43:33,738
mojim verenikom, kapetanom
Gustavom Moranteom?

446
00:43:33,823 --> 00:43:36,823
Sada je u generaltabu u Panami.

447
00:43:40,413 --> 00:43:43,413
Narednie, donesite knjigu!

448
00:43:50,048 --> 00:43:53,048
Doite.

449
00:43:59,891 --> 00:44:02,351
Evo, pogledajte.

450
00:44:02,352 --> 00:44:05,352
Pie crno na belom.

451
00:44:05,355 --> 00:44:08,355
Otila je u prestonicu
da potrai posao.

452
00:44:08,566 --> 00:44:11,566
Bez para i polugola.

453
00:44:12,111 --> 00:44:15,527
Bila je luda. -Mogu li da
razgovaram sa njenim bratom?

454
00:44:15,698 --> 00:44:19,447
ao mi je, premeten je.
-Gde?

455
00:44:20,703 --> 00:44:23,788
To je poverljiva informacija.

456
00:44:24,999 --> 00:44:28,700
Mi smo u vanrednom stanju.

457
00:45:18,344 --> 00:45:21,344
Narednik Rivera?
-Vama na usluzi.

458
00:45:21,764 --> 00:45:24,764
Ja sam Irena...
-Znam ko ste.

459
00:45:28,062 --> 00:45:31,182
Mogu li da vam kupim pivo?
-Zato da ne?

460
00:45:41,200 --> 00:45:44,200
Pivo, molim.

461
00:46:02,138 --> 00:46:06,431
Izvinite.
-Ne idi tako brzo.

462
00:46:08,102 --> 00:46:11,102
Gledaj kakva je.
-Aha.

463
00:46:17,403 --> 00:46:20,672
Primetila sam da ste bili...

464
00:46:20,673 --> 00:46:23,942
pogoeni i rastueni
onog dana

465
00:46:24,535 --> 00:46:27,535
kod Evanhelinine kue.

466
00:46:27,580 --> 00:46:29,769
Niste kao Ramirez.

467
00:46:29,770 --> 00:46:31,959
Znam ga kao svoj dlan.

468
00:46:31,960 --> 00:46:34,878
Da li je komandir uvek
tako nesmotren?

469
00:46:34,879 --> 00:46:37,068
Mislim...

470
00:46:37,069 --> 00:46:39,258
ona pucnjava me je
nasmrt preplaila.

471
00:46:39,259 --> 00:46:42,219
Nije bio takav.

472
00:46:42,220 --> 00:46:45,220
Nije lo ovek, kunem se.

473
00:46:53,940 --> 00:46:56,940
Za ene kao to ste vi.

474
00:47:07,996 --> 00:47:11,578
